summary: This Mod Add An New House Near Whiterun
descriptionHtml:
This Mod Add A New House Called Miania Manor Located At Whiterun Hold.
This Mod Doesnt Require HeartFire DLC!!!

This Player House Contain:
-Over 50 Custom Chest (A Storage With A Custom Chest).
-10+ Mannequin In The Basement
-2 Secret Room
-A Few Guard To Protect Your House.
-A Tower

Example Of Custom Chest
-Potion Chest
-Enchanted Heavy Armor Collection
-Food Supply
-And Alot More

Note:
-Container Named "Trash Barrel" is a respawnable container that means the item u put in there will respawn or gone.so just put your unwanted item here.
-This Mod Nearly Completed (Not Yet Done,ABout 98%) i'm gonna Finish And fix bug whenever i can.
